OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772809881
OL,3,CBristol social media 'School Wars'
OL,4,Ctrend blamed for attack on 12-year-old
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FThe family of 12-year-old girl
OL,8,Fattacked at a central Bristol school
OL,9,Fsay the violence was enflamed by a so-
OL,10,Fcalled 'School Wars' social media post
OL,11,Fbeing shared by young teenagers in
OL,12,FBristol.
OL,14,FThe post lists Bristol secondary
OL,15,Fschools on 'red' or 'blue' sides, and
OL,16,Fassociated posts have encouraged
OL,17,Forganised violence between schools on
OL,18,Fopposing sides. Similar posts have
OL,19,Fappeared for schools in Cardiff,
OL,20,FBirmingham and London.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
