FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772809881
OL,3,CBristol social media 'School Wars'
OL,4,Ctrend blamed for attack on 12-year-old
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FIn footage viewed by ITV News, the 12-
OL,8,Fyear-old girl is repeatedly punched in
OL,9,Fthe face at her 'blue' school by a 13-
OL,10,Fyear-old boy from a 'red' school. He
OL,11,Falso attacks other children present.
OL,13,FWe have spoken to the girl's 17-year-
OL,14,Fold sister who wishes to remain
OL,15,Fanonymous, for fear of reprisals. She
OL,16,Fsays the 'School Wars' trend presents
OL,17,Fa real danger to children, whether
OL,18,Fthey want to be involved or not, and
OL,19,Fbelieves it has provoked other violent
OL,20,Fincidents in Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772809881
OL,3,CBristol social media 'School Wars'
OL,4,Ctrend blamed for attack on 12-year-old
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,F"Whether you're red side or blue side,
OL,8,Fyou're automatically someone that
OL,9,Fsomebody will look at and say, 'Yeah,
OL,10,Flet's get him.' That's what these kids
OL,11,Fthink and it's disgusting", she told
OL,12,Fus.
OL,14,FLast week headteachers at several
OL,15,FBristol schools contacted parents
OL,16,Fabout the viral post, asking them to
OL,17,Fcheck their children's phones for
OL,18,Fmaterial relating to 'School Wars'.
OL,19,FAvon & Somerset Police organised extra
OL,20,Fpatrols around schools.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
