OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772809881
OL,3,CBristol social media 'School Wars'
OL,4,Ctrend blamed for attack on 12-year-old
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FShadene Keeling, a Bristol youth
OL,8,Fjustice practitioner dealing with
OL,9,Fviolent children, says social media is
OL,10,Foften at the heart of the behaviour
OL,11,Fshe sees: "It encourages them to get
OL,12,Finvolved, or jump on whatever trend is
OL,13,Fout there at the current time.
OL,14,FChildren are highly influenced by
OL,15,Fsocial media, so it's imperative, to
OL,16,Fsave children's lives, that parents
OL,17,Ftake action now."
OL,19,FThe UK government is currently
OL,20,Fconsulting on banning social media for
OL,21,Funder-16s.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
